Class ShufflingDataSetIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.dl4j.ShufflingDataSetIterator

    public class ShufflingDataSetIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.nd4j.linalg.dataset.api.iterator.DataSetIterator, java.io.Serializable
    An nd4j mini-batch iterator that shuffles the data whenever it is reset.
